Ofelia it's a codename for Open-ended Front-end

Ofelia will stands as building round for those who are interested in developing 
applications on top of ZendFramework.

We will develop the basic tools:

- HTML
- Basic CSS
- Session and User control interfaces (login/logout, profiles, ACLs, etc)
- Database connections
- Logging

Don't forget to use the zf-tool to generate new controllers/views/modules/models. 

Please, participate! ;)

LinuxCabal's PHPCabal group
http://linuxcabal.org/
